 safety. The opposite of collapse_teaches_better_future. Requires the undiscounted far future. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 8 suffering_focused → 13 collapse_degrades_future" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWGtT4zgW%2FSu3qJ3dpBeC7bzDMlV0E2a6Fnq6gN6pqaYrrdhKosGxvJJNyPYwv32PZDtxiCnSky9UkKVzz33qXn07CPiEpWHyTgb8YHBwfEynp6d0q5iIKJHkK%2Fa%2FJX4sIrpLPcdt0UKqMHgQfEELd%2BSN2qPOqDdym1TTiYzJbdYNwF0EoDOt03mcCBmRPwPegByKmZL%2BTLDQwLl9j1yaMDViC7YczdI5i3TxwSMWiTkL9UjLOV%2FMWFJ8adMkTVLF8wOjOUsSrkYLkcxGgdC%2BTKNERNNie4ciWV4fbZwudvVIp5MJV3aD9FPNgxXFJvkyDFms%2BSjgU8UCrnMQq%2BeQ%2BTNia2WFJkYfl8kMvyci5ARTrj%2FrY0qMMiwI9CEpDvuLiGuSyoIpfgQbsTmHSkJjPZnxzHz%2F0NA78i3GCRjNY6mNmqsNOBsFHIhYEtqi6YRFAQtlxGkOB4cN%2Brry3%2FDhq6FqjvPHmPsJDj6wMOUkJxZh7eqGBXvLdULjdEmpEWMOal5WbEBnl5cXw%2FNs90%2FDD8Prs9vhOY2XNOURVyzhjXhZxBEPRLJhljf4eAhfJZlwYzkgWaxPkc9VYlScS4XYWVlIZ3sz9Vkch4LrBt0s541QTiOpED%2B1b3H7kOJ%2B%2B6lusax3%2Bs4P9O79id055gnLVmMlx2wsQpGAyFgaNQOTBJ%2BdQ3K%2FNOiC%2BYmETJY7XmBDbGweJYekJXETCFJN4anh58X52eVvx3%2F7QmMeygWi3Jy1HuWP%2BB0ucRzYsKLFguwg9ZPM9vAWR2xC%2FUkoU5yawdHneQjT6baCSK2G07Nqmp%2B9pzqRDSZgQocFF9MZsJGIijObHDNYy8SdptqtnDMt7k%2FoP1DIfPMcz4GxVgnxUQlQT5bVkt2GmwvuNNq5YP6YKFYSyx7gPwMNnXmEsFlhvyw%2By7CS1q6FjrF4lIg5p3%2BSzxKmEyVjWMwUgShlNgNN4jF1lCHkQV27ZnPNl8c3CJuI%2FnR%2BOF4qetD0QapgxlJNf7qNtlk8gaBTxCEVNQNcivy%2FsIhXqJfCxJqqtoiX26Pt5ObYIgMvr0zCYAz1IB7YGKWiEAQE%2BEbMhU6EDz8qrKPE2o0mBJHY0wgJVR%2FQjzA%2Fo1D69zw4Qhoga2Fgm7t5%2BpwLhfQmDpP71h2lQI0ViqxaIkojFCJf4PchvR1e%2FHI9zJLNImSeBFuIMpkyR0mOkiNUXn%2BG%2BFrpTzefrq7Orn%2FLwhhVLhMCMiBnkcYy4T7VTHzT2Ydz2EMJhvTOsqLeoFv4cpJC2yxjjsbLo%2BwXoejAStbBWQ3JqKHsZwpl26xO8oFHFhXlD5mZKvzM604oHpCD5naDoFBEBTH931RMpyE%2Ftgz18b9E8GOjWMyqp01yVC0UC1O9oDhgfvkwpDhkmay8hLPAFD0ODy%2FXRRTFnkGmKZzQXUSQbRFQBLKdWYVG3sk0%2Frcwlo3OWbj8yNUnHVRHWqfR8fr9Zq%2Fd77les%2Bu4%2FMhpr8qA47jdfq%2FbbLlOt9t2va7bygPymf9QhG0Q5MXHEBjdZww2HPb35%2B46yVy19sxgy45lsJU976