 optimism: hazard is high during the AI / nuclear transition but collapses once decorrelated, self-sufficient settlements exist — no single catastrophe reaches them all. The window closes, the expected future stretches far past the background-hazard baseline, and x-risk reduction during the window is what unlocks it (Ord, The Precipice; the multiplanetary-backup argument). Mutually exclusive with the view that early expansion re-arms the hazard. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 8 suffering_focused → 13 collapse_degrades_future → 14 time_of_perils_exit" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWf1z2zYS%2FVd2PNc7KWfLpL5lnzvjxHKbqfMxtnOdTpxRIBKScKYIHkBaVtP0b%2B8DQEqURU%2BU6peMQgJv3z7sLnbpLwchn7AsSl%2FJkB%2BcHBwf09nZGd0qJmJKJQWK%2Fb7Ej0VMd1nT89u0kCoKHwRf0MIfNUedUXfUH%2FmtEV7VdCoT8tt1g3EXA%2Btc62yepELGFMwAeUIeJUzJYCZYZBD9QZN8mjA1Ygu2HM2yOYt18aJJLBZzFumRlnO%2BmLG0eNOhSZZmiucbRnOWplyNFiKdjUKhA5nFqYinxfIuxbL8fLSxu1jVJ51NJlzZBTLINA9XFFsUyChiieajkE8VC7nOQVZL2pSKOR%2FJySgBBkjzR5FaFYYsmBFbSyE0MXq%2FTGf4PRERJ2i9fq2PKTWusjDUh6Q4DkjEXJNUFkzxIyjI5hwOC43n6Yw7cf%2BloUocWIxT8J0nUhsRVguwNw45EPFIaIumUxaHLJIxpzkiIGrQ59UBDx8%2BG6pmO39MeJBi4wOLMk5yYhHWsdCwYC%2B5TmmcLSkzZsxGzcuOndD51dXl8MKt%2Fmn4dnh9fju8oPGSpjzmiqW8kSyLQOOhSDdkeYGXhzjJ1Bk3ygHJYn2IA65S4%2BJcKkTWSiHt1jr3WZJEgusG3SznjUhOY6kQXbUvSeeQkkHna91i2dMZeD%2FQq9enduWYp8w9TZQcs7GIRAoiY2ncDE2WfPQOyf%2FUoEsWpBI2meIOCgsSo3mcHpKWxE0gSDXFSQ0%2FLi7Or347%2FscnGvNILpADZq89Uf6I39ES24ENFS0WbIdZkDrtcVockQv3J5HMsGuGg77IA5zOth1E4jW8vnXT%2FOx%2FrRPZYAImfFhwMZ0BG2mqOLOpM4NaJu401W7lnGlxf0r%2FhUPmXdNrehBrlS7vlQD1dFlt2W%2F4ueFuo5Mb5o%2BpYiWz7AHnZ6DhM48RNivs5827%2FCt57VvoBA%2BPTCrSvylgKdOpkgkUMyUizpjNQJN4TB3lGeyCunbN5povj28QNjH96f1wvFT0oOmtVOGMZZr%2B9Bsd8%2FAUhs4Qh1RUFHApqsOlRXyDgipMrKlqRZq5Hh0vl2OLDE55JQmDGOpBPLAxSkVhCAg4GzEXOhUBzlHhOQqwXWhCEIk9jZFQ9RP6EfIzimRwz8MjpAGyFgLb3L2LXa0aolTtSrpVkNYBi%2FhRlhQhuSoSuSfCPZ6x35lCiOHwEOZBJE2Isw