ed-value reasoning that bought astronomical stakes now attenuates them: future-facing value is multiplied by the probability the simulation keeps running, and the ranking slides back toward the present. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 8 suffering_focused → 13 collapse_degrades_future → 15 space_expansion_backfires → 16 living_in_simulation" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWX9v2zgS%2FSqD4PbO7sWOZMe%2FkssCaePsFpd2iyS9YtEULi3RNi%2BSqCOluN5u97PfIynZcuwgbv1P4UrUmzePM8MZ5utByCcsj7JXMuQHJwdHR3R2dka3iomEMkmBYn8s8GOe0F3e8vxjmksVhQ%2BCz2nuj1qjzqg76o%2F89sjvjPwu1XQmU%2FK7dQNzlwDuXOs8TjMhEwpmQD0hj1KmZDATLDKg%2FqBFPk2YGrE5W4xmecwSXb5oEUtEzCI90jLm8xnLyjcdmuRZrnjxwShmWcbVaC6y2SgUOpB5kolkWi7vUiKrz0drX5er%2BqTzyYQru0AGuebhkmKbAhlFLNV8FPKpYiHXBchySYd0ygI%2B4l9SgMLl0ZgF9xOh%2BNICNIrEg8EXyUiLOI%2BY0cZKNWTBjNhKL6GJ0btFNsPviYg4YU9Wr%2FURZUYPFob6kBTHRooEhqSyYIo3IDOLOVQRGs%2BzGXc78A8N6ZLAYpzCqTiV2ii1XIBvk5ADEY%2BEtmg6Y0nIIplwihEpUZM%2BLwNh%2BPDZUDWfw3EeZPjwgUU5JzmxCKuYaVqwl1xnNM4XlBsz5kPNq46d0PnV1eXwwq3%2BZfh2eH1%2BO7yg8YKmPOGKZbyZLsqA5KHI1mR5gZeH2O7MGTfKAclivU8CrjLjYiwVwm%2BpkHZrnfssTSPBdZNuFnEzktNEKoRg7WvaOaR00PlWt1h2dwbeT%2FTq9aldOeYZc09TJcdsLCKRgchYGjdDk00fvUPyPzXpkgWZhE2muIPCgtRonmSHpCVxEwhSTbFTw4%2Fzi%2FOr34%2F%2B9onGPJJzJIr51u4o%2F4Lf0QKfAxsqWizYDvMgc9pjtzgiEe5PIpnjqxk2%2BqLIAjrbdBDZ2fT61k3zs%2F%2BtTmSDCZjwYc7FdAZs5LLizObXDGqZuNNUu5Ux0%2BL%2BlP4Dh8y7ltfyINYyp94pAerZYrtlv%2BkXhrvNTmGYf8kUq5hlD9g%2FAw2feYKwWWI%2Fbd4lacVr30KneNjIRMzpnxSwjOlMyRSKmTqS5DYrjUUUpkaR5i6oa9cs1nxxdIOwSegv76ejhaIHTW%2BlCmcs1%2FSX3%%2BEotSKEgUwsUgoQbqvh9SC%2BHl79dD109swguWRAQ2E1TjGIcnEnWwPkYzKD4cqvo5v2bN%2BfXv7tKgYPEGcF%2BY%2F8t0lhmPKCaKSF0%2FvYCIacEQwV1hafepFvjVo6AckWpMV403C9CXUcgWkGcr44adsA55JZZn%2BQDTywqThgUv1wFvNQHJyU0Fy5mIpGUxPT%2FcjGdRvzIMtRH%2FxLhz83yoTugbB3FwYB6bA4IOA6Y394OKY2Ys1Wckiw05wpHEi1W5xTOUwabZuPgu0hg2yKgzrqV7hBEjMg8%2FbcwyiYXLFq84%2Bq9DrcnRbfZbQ0G7X5n0Pdb7Z7n84b