+ suffering_focused + collapse_degrades_future + space_expansion_backfires + living_in_simulation + person_affecting_view&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Person-affecting population ethics: making happy people is neutral, so the astronomical case for x-risk reduction — which rests on the sheer number of extra future lives saved from extinction — loses almost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 8 suffering_focused → 13 collapse_degrades_future → 15 space_expansion_backfires → 16 living_in_simulation → 17 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJy1WWtT20gW%2FSu3qJ1dm8FGsvELlqkiAWZSSzIUkE1NhZTTltp2D5Ja2y1hPJnkt%2B%2Fp1sMyFoUz1HyhhNR97rnv2%2B0vOz6fsjRIXkuf7xzu7O%2FT8fEx3SgmIkokeYr9scTDIqLbtOO4B7SQKvDvBV%2FQwh13xr1xfzwcu92x2xu7%2FbE7oIZOZEzuoGmQbiMgnmidhnEiZETeHMCH5FDMlPTmggUG1x11yKUpU2O2YMvxPA1ZpIsPHWKRCFmgx1qGfDFnSfGlR9M0SRXPN4xDliRcjRcimY99oT2ZRomIZsXyPkWy%2Bn68trtYNSSdTqdc2QXSSzX3S4pd8mQQsFjzsc9nivlc5yDlkh7pmHl8zB9igELl8YR5d1OheCnB7VMg7g2%2BiMZahGnArG2KzwOKudLYycDDs0yNva0pz5g3J7ayp9DE6HKZzPE8FQEnuG31We9TYuzFfF%2FvkeLwtYhARCoLpngLbmAhh9WExvtkzjMP%2FUvDtJFnMY6gdBhLbSxZLsDeyOdAxCuhLZpOWOSzQEacQgRT0KbPZayc3X82VM12GAZKYeM9C1JOcmoRVmHVtmCvuE5oki4pNWLMRs2rih3SDbB%2BMZ7jdMHZLOXZxp%2FP3p1dndycndJkSTMeccUS3o6XRfhyXyRrFtrFxz1ERpLxMEYEksV6H3lcJUbbUCpEamksna3NLMHiOBBct%2Bl6GbYDOYukQrQ2vsS9PYpHva9Ni2UdNXJ%2BoNdvjuzKCU9Y9jZWcsImIhAJiEyk0dg3uffR2SP3U5vOmZdIyGSKZ1BYEBvzR8keaUncxIRUMzjt7OPi9OTit%2F1%2FfKIJD%2BQCOWX2WufyBzwHS2wHNgxqsSDbT70kcwMcxxG0UH8ayBS75vD5aZ4wdLypIBK57QytmuZx%2BLVJZOMKmNBhwcVsDmykveLMpuIc1jIhqKlx