t;If most observers like us are simulated, the astronomical future that justified x-risk work probably gets switched off long before it happens. The same expected-value reasoning that bought astronomical stakes now attenuates them: future-facing value is multiplied by the probability the simulation keeps running, and the ranking slides back toward the present. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 8 suffering_focused → 13 collapse_degrades_future → 16 living_in_simulation" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWH9z2zYS%2FSo7nuudlLNlUrJ%2BOefOOLHcZs5OM7ZznU6cUSASktCQBA8gLevS9LPfA0BKlEVPlOofj0wCb98%2B7C52%2BeUg5FOWR9lrGfKD04PjYzo7O6M7xURCmaRAsf8t8WOR0H3e9vwTWkgVhQ%2BCL2jhj9vj7rg3Hoz9ztjvUUNnMiW%2F1zQY9wmwzrXO4zQTMqFgDshT8ihlSgZzwSKD6A%2Fb5NOUqTFbsOV4nscs0eWLNrFExCzSYy1jvpizrHzTpWme5YoXG8YxyzKuxguRzceh0IHMk0wks3J5jxJZfT7e2F2uGpDOp1Ou7AIZ5JqHK4odCmQUsVTzcchnioVcFyCrJT2KxIPZK5KxFnEeMeO3lWHEgjmxtRZCE6N3y2yO31MRcYLY69f6mDLjKwtDfUiK44REwjVJZcEUP4KELObwWGg8z%2BbcqfsPDVmSwGK8BOE4ldqosFqAvUnIgYhHQls0nbEkZJFMOMUIgahFn1YnPHr4ZKia7fwx5UGGjQ8syjnJqUVYB0PLgr3iOqNJvqTcmDEbNa86dkrnV1eXowu3%2BqfR29HN%2Bd3ogiZLmvGEK5bxVrosI42HItuQ5QVeHuIoM2fcKAcki%2FU%2BCbjKjIuxVAitlULarXXuszSNBNctul3GrUjOEqkQXo0vafeQ0mH3a9Ni2dMZej%2FQ6zcv7coJz5h7mio5YRMRiQxEJtK4GZo0%2BeAdkv%2BxRZcsyCRsMsUdFBakRvMkOyQtiZtAkGqGkxp9WFycX%2F12%2FLePNOGRXCAJzF57ovwRv6MltgMbKlos2A7zIHPa47Q4QhfuTyOZY9ccB31RRDidbTuIzGt5A%2Bum%2BTn42iSywQRM%2BLDgYjYHNvJUcWZzZw61TNxpatzJmGnx%2BSX9Bw6Zd22v7UGsVb68UwLUs2W9Zb%2FlF4Z7rW5hmD9milXMsgecn4GGzzxB2KywnzfvErDitW%2BhUzw8ykTM6Z8UsIzpTMkUipkakeQ2K41FFJ2jIoVdUDduWKz58vgWYZPQn94Px0tFD5reShXOWa7pT7%2FVNQ9fwtAZ4pDKkgIuZXm4tIjXqKjCxJqqV6Rd6NH1Cjm2yOCUV5IwiKEexAOboFSUhoCAsxGx0JkIcI4Kz1GB7UITgkjsWYKEap7Sj5CfUSSDzzw8QhogayGwzV2c4apUvZamOOaIv7NV2Dewdegovmusl5LKUTdRNWbEE5nP5jSVNt%2BNI0VtbpZ5%2FEqaE4hxal6nSNcLoVBOiOOIA3v8lcRIFWq%2BWiIrEhS%2BQOD3Ib0aXf5yM3LJbRFc5EAduGYyM8YNkWRHuAiC